text:
A tree node for yield expressions used in generator functions.

 For example:

 function* id(){
     var index = 0;
     while(index < 10)
         yield index++;
 }

methods.description:
Is this a yield * expression in a generator function?

 For example:

 function* id(){
     yield 1;
     yield * anotherGeneratorFunc();
     yield 10;
 }
